# Ability Name	Unique Key				Category of Ability		Type						Define					Description																																																																																Modify VAR																				Source Page
Animated Hair	KEY:Animated Hair ~ Korred	CATEGORY:Special Ability	TYPE:SpecialAttack.Supernatural	DEFINE:KorredAnimatedHairDC|0		DESC:A korred's hair is constantly writhing and twitching.  As a free action, a korred can cause its long hair to reach out and interfere with adjacent creatures - tugging at clothes and weapons, tangling feet and arms, tickllling, and generally making a nuisance of itself.  The korred can select which adjacent targets are affected by its animated hair.  These targets must make a successful DC %1 Reflex save each round to avoid becoming entangled for 1 round.|KorredAnimatedHairDC	BONUS:VAR|KorredAnimatedHairDC|10+TL/2+DEX	BONUS:VAR|KorredAnimatedHairDC|2|PREFEAT:1,Ability Focus (Animated Hair)	SOURCEPAGE:p.173
Stone Stride	KEY:Stone Stride ~ Korred	CATEGORY:Special Ability	TYPE:SpecialQuality.Supernatural							DESC:This ability works like tree stride, except it requires loose boulders at least as large as the korred, and only has a range of 30 feet.  The korred can use this ability once per round as a standard action.																																																																			SOURCEPAGE:p.173
Stunning Laugh	KEY:Stunning Laugh ~ Korred	CATEGORY:Special Ability	TYPE:SpecialAttack.Supernatural	DEFINE:KorredStunningLaughDC|0	DESC:Three times per day as a standard action, a korred can unleash a strange laugh that stuns all creatures within a 30-foot burst for 1d2 rounds (Fortitude DC %1 negates).  This is a sonic, mind-affecting effect.  Fey are immune to this ability.|KorredStunningLaughDC																																					BONUS:VAR|KorredStunningLaughDC|10+TL/2+CHA	BONUS:VAR|KorredStunningLaughDC|2|PREFEAT:1,Ability Focus (Stunning Laugh)	SOURCEPAGE:p.173

