Wisdom Drain											KEY:Wisdom Drain ~ Lamia Matriarch					CATEGORY:Special Ability	TYPE:SpecialAttack.Supernatural	DEFINE:LamiaMatriarchWisdomDrainDC|0	DESC:A lama matriarch drains 1d4 points of Wisdom each time she hits with her melee touch attack.  The first time each round that she strikes a foe with a melee weapon, she also drains 1 point of Wisdom.  A DC %1 Will save negates the Wisdom drain.  Unlike with other kinds of ability drain attacks, a lamia matriarch does not heal damage when she uses her Wisdom drain.|LamiaMatriarchWisdomDrainDC	BONUS:VAR|LamiaMatriarchWisdomDrainDC|10+TL/2+CHA	BONUS:VAR|LamiaMatriarchWisdomDrainDC|2|PREFEAT:1,Ability Focus (Wisdom Drain)	SOURCEPAGE:p.175	ASPECT:Ability Benefit|(touch 1d4, weapon 1 point on first hit each round)
