Leprechaun Magic	CATEGORY:Special Ability	TYPE:SpecialQuality.SpellLike	DESC:When a leprechaun uses any of its spell-like abilities to deceive, trick, or humiliate a creature (at the GM's discretion), the spell-like ability resolves at caster level 8th rather than 4th.  If a leprechaun uses its spell-like abilities in this manner, it has a bonus of +11 on concentration checks.	SOURCEPAGE:p.177

